com.ca.mas.identity.group

Class MASOwner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ca.mas.identity.group.MASOwner

  • public class MASOwner
extends java.lang.Object

    MASOwner is a thinly wrapped User object that represents the one and only owner of an ad-hoc group.

    "owner": { "value": "string", "ref": "string", "display": "string" }
